<a href='http://www.ukclimbing.com/articles/page.php?id=8765' title='Read full article'><img src='https://cdn.ukclimbing.com/t/288569.jpg' width='150' height='105' alt='thumb' border='1' align='left' hspace='8' /></a>The Grivel Air Tech crampon is a lightweight, semi-rigid all season crampon.This 12 point crampon is ideal for use in both Scottish winter mountaineering as well as classic and technical Alpinism. 



The Air Tech weighs 790 grams per crampon and folds up into itself so it takes up minimal space in your pack. Over all the Air Tech is a great all rounder for everything but steep difficult ice routes. 